        dd
          u 台
        dd <ruby>外<rt>&thinsp;ㆣㄨㄚ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>國<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㆦㆶ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>錢<rt>&thinsp;ㄐㆳˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(<ruby>匯<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>率<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄨㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>換<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄢ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>算<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄨㄢ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>新<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄣ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>台<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄞˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>票<rt>&thinsp;ㄆ丨ㄜ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>一<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(<ruby>美<rt>&thinsp;ㆠ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>元<rt>&thinsp;ㆣㄨㄢˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>對<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>四<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>十<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄚㆴ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。→<ruby>一<rt>&thinsp;丨ㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>對<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨ丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>二<rt>&thinsp;ㆢ丨˫/ㄌ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>十<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄚㆴ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>七<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。
