    div
      h3 <ruby>掌<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄤˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>上<rt>&thinsp;ㄕㄤˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>明<rt>&thinsp;ㄇ丨ㄥˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>珠<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄨ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>
      dl
        dd None
        dd
          u 國語
        dd (成) 掌上珠。<ruby>比<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>喻<rt>&thinsp;ㆡㄨ˫/ㄌㄨ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：<ruby>稱<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>呼<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㆦ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>極<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨ㆤㆶ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>其<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨ˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>受<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄨ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>父<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㆤ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>母<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㄨˋ/ㆠㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>疼<rt>&thinsp;ㄊ丨ㆩ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>惜<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄜㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>丌<rt>&thinsp;˙ㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>女<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄨˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>兒<rt>&thinsp;ㆢ丨ˊ/ㄌ丨ˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>查<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄚ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>某<rt>&thinsp;ㆠㆦˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>囝<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨ㆩˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)。<ruby>意<rt>&thinsp;丨˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>思<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄨ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>惜<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㄜㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby><mark>&#xffa42;</mark><rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>那<rt>&thinsp;ㄋㄚˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(若也)<ruby>像<rt>&thinsp;ㄑ丨ㆫ˫/ㄑ丨ㆧ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>一<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>粒<rt>&thinsp;ㄌ丨ㄚㆴ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>美<rt>&thinsp;ㆠ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>珠<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄨ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。→<ruby>得<rt>&thinsp;ㄉ丨ㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>人<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>愛<rt>&thinsp;ㄞ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>丌<rt>&thinsp;˙ㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>物<rt>&thinsp;ㄇ丨ㆷ̇/ㄇㆭㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>件<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨ㆩ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。→(套語)。

