    div
      h3 <ruby>易<rt>&thinsp;丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>如<rt>&thinsp;ㄖㄨˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>反<rt>&thinsp;ㄈㄢˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>掌<rt>&thinsp;ㄓㄤˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>
