        dd (成語) (台)<ruby>鶴<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄜㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>雖<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄨ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>鳥<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>不<rt>&thinsp;ㆬ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>食<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>用<rt>&thinsp;丨ㆲ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>供<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨ㆲ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>玩<rt>&thinsp;ㄨㄢˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>賞<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨ㆧˋ/ㄒ丨ㆫˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(漳/泉)<ruby>丌<rt>&thinsp;˙ㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>琴<rt>&thinsp;ㄎ丨ㆬˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>雖<rt>&thinsp;ㄙㄨ丨&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>一<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>片<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㆳˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>柴<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>頭<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>不<rt>&thinsp;ㆬ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>起<rt>&thinsp;ㄎ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>火<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㆤˋ/ㄏㆤˋ/ㄏㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>柴<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>是<rt>&thinsp;ㄒ丨˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>供<rt>&thinsp;ㄍ丨ㆲ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>奏<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄠ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>出<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄨㆵ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>美<rt>&thinsp;ㆠ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>妙<rt>&thinsp;ㆠ丨ㄠ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>丌<rt>&thinsp;˙ㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>音<rt>&thinsp;丨ㆬ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>樂<rt>&thinsp;ㆣㄚㆶ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>不<rt>&thinsp;ㆬ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>知<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄞ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>價<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㆤ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>值<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄚㆵ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/<ruby>路<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㆦ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>用<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄥ˫/丨ㆲ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby>)<ruby>丌<rt>&thinsp;˙ㆤ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>人<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄤˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>刣<rt>&thinsp;ㄊㄞˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>鶴<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄜㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>起<rt>&thinsp;ㄎ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>來<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㄞˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>食<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㄚㆷ̇&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>將<rt>&thinsp;ㄐ丨ㆲ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>琴<rt>&thinsp;ㄎ丨ㆬˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>當<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㆲ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>做<rt>&thinsp;ㄗㄨㆤ˪/ㄗㄜ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>起<rt>&thinsp;ㄎ丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>火<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㆤˋ/ㄏㆤˋ/ㄏㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>柴<rt>&thinsp;ㄘㄚˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>、<ruby>烆<rt>&thinsp;ㄏ丨ㆩˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>火<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㆤˋ/ㄏㆤˋ/ㄏㄜˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。比喻：殺風景的行為。「煮」的類語：<ruby>焙<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄟˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：～香。
