        dd <ruby>炮<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：～羊肉。水～肚兒。～肉。趙典音「<rt>ㄅㄠˋ</rt>」，<ruby>～<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>魚片。<ruby>煲<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：～粥。<ruby>炮<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：～<ruby>肚<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。<ruby>煲<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：雞～飯。～<ruby>肚<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>兒。<ruby>爆<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄠˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：～<ruby>肚<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄨˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>兒。～炒。～香。～米花。<ruby>拌<rt>&thinsp;ㄅㄢˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>：～和。～攪。<ruby>煸<rt>&thinsp;ㄅ丨ㄢ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>(/編)：～鍋。～菜，～肉。
