        dd <ruby>牽<rt>&thinsp;ㄎㄢ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>滷<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㆦˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>拍<rt>&thinsp;ㄆㄚㆷ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>滷<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㆦˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>，<ruby>蓋<rt>&thinsp;ㄍㄞ˪&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>滷<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㆦˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>、<ruby>企<rt>&thinsp;ㄎ丨ㄚ˫&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>滷<rt>&thinsp;ㄌㆦˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>。
        dd
